{"ts": "2026-05-09T08:45:31.357490+00:00", "runtime_id": "social-tom-llm-structured", "target_slot": null, "turn_index": 1, "prompt": "You extract Theory-of-Mind observations from one dialogue turn.\nReturn a JSON array. Each item must have exactly these fields:\n[\n  {\n    \"target_slot\": \"belief_about_other|intent_about_other|feeling_about_other|preference_about_other\",\n    \"summary\": \"short stable claim\",\n    \"detail\": \"specific evidence-aware detail\",\n    \"evidence\": \"short quote or observation from the user message\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.0,\n    \"control_signal\": 0.0\n  }\n]\n\nDo not infer demographics. Do not output markdown. If there is no clear Theory-of-Mind observation, return [].\n\nUser message:\n\"\"\"\nHi. Coming back after a tough week. I wanted to pick up where we left off when I shared about feeling stuck.\n\"\"\"", "raw_output": "```json\n[]\n```", "parsed_count": 0, "parse_status": "parse_error", "parse_error": "Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)"}
{"ts": "2026-05-09T08:48:05.971621+00:00", "runtime_id": "common-ground-llm-structured", "target_slot": null, "turn_index": 1, "prompt": "Extract common-ground observations from one dialogue turn.\nReturn a JSON array. Each item must have exactly these fields:\n[\n  {\n    \"scope_kind\": \"dyad|group\",\n    \"scope_id\": \"stable dyad or group id\",\n    \"summary\": \"shared fact or mutual acceptance\",\n    \"accepted_by_ids\": [\"id1\", \"id2\"],\n    \"evidence\": \"short quote or observation\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.0,\n    \"recursion_depth\": 2,\n    \"control_signal\": 0.0\n  }\n]\n\nOnly include facts mutually accepted or clearly shared. Do not infer common ground from keywords alone. If none is clear, return [].\n\nUser message:\n\"\"\"\nHi. Coming back after a tough week. I wanted to pick up where we left off when I shared about feeling stuck.\n\"\"\"", "raw_output": "```json\n[\n  {\n    \"scope_kind\": \"dyad\",\n    \"scope_id\": \"user_and_ai\",\n    \"summary\": \"The user and AI acknowledge they were discussing the same topic.\",\n    \"accepted_by_ids\": [\"user\", \"ai\"],\n    \"evidence\": \"I wanted to pick up where we left off when I shared about feeling stuck.\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.95,\n    \"recursion_depth\": 2,\n    \"control_signal\": 0.85\n  }\n]\n```", "parsed_count": 0, "parse_status": "parse_error", "parse_error": "Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0)"}
